OOC: Never accept damage? Apparently you havent seen many of my posts.

BIC:
As Shadowstar latches onto the blade of energy with his mouth, Zero quickly 
deactivates it freeing it from his jaws. He then points his left arm at 
Shadowstar and opens fire on him with six blasts from his wrist blast as he 
reactivates the beam sabre and slashes upwards at Shadowstars neck.
